  "2298620": {
    "name": "英灵战士自走棋",
    "steam_appid": 2298620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瓦尔哈拉在召唤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建你的矮人部落，带领他们踏上荣耀的征程吧！向村庄发起战争，根据敌人的特点调整你的阵容和战略，前排的肉盾战士吸引火力，而后排的法师和弓箭手则施以致命一击。洗劫这些村庄，收集战利品来加强你的部落，然后去挑战更强大的敌人，创造属于你的英雄史诗，让无尽的战场见证你的荣光！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建立你的荣耀部落</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一支小而无畏的维京矮人团队开始，将他们发展成一支不可阻挡的力量！通过不断的战争和掠夺来提升他们的能力，并招募新的战士加入你的部落！每个矮人战士都可以进行专属定制，根据不同的装备和技能，他们可以成长为强大的狂战士、机智的先知、敏捷的刺客或威力强大的法师，让你的战士们通过战斗的洗礼，成长为各自角色类别的传奇英雄！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298620/extras/6fe3c7816861799e046e158c2033ee2e.poster.avif?t=1772096278\" width=600 height=483 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298620/extras/6fe3c7816861799e046e158c2033ee2e.webm?t=1772096278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >英雄的进阶之旅</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个神秘的世界中，你的战士们可以通过战争获得前所未有的力量：技能、装备升级、传奇武器、锻造、还有宠物同伴！在这片古老的土地上，这些力量将成为你征服之路上的重要助力。面对强大无比的敌人，只有运用精妙的策略和战术，才能让你在这片战场上所向披靡！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298620/extras/816f1190ab3784193e037a674a68cb93.poster.avif?t=1772096278\" width=600 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298620/extras/816f1190ab3784193e037a674a68cb93.webm?t=1772096278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >征服与荣耀之路</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上这条征服与荣耀之路，你将带领你的矮人部落挑战诸多神秘而强大的敌人。随着你的每一步前进，你将解锁新的战场，面对更加凶险的对手，从森林、火地到沙漠、雪山，每一个地点都蕴藏着未知的挑战和难以想象的财富。在这片大地上创造你的传奇，让英雄的赞歌成为你荣耀的见证！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298620/extras/056fac50c4990b31eff0e0d3272ff1ad.poster.avif?t=1772096278\" width=600 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298620/extras/056fac50c4990b31eff0e0d3272ff1ad.webm?t=1772096278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为了英灵殿的荣耀</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在，是时候响应这场史诗般的召唤，加入《英灵战士自走棋》的战斗了！在这场史诗战役中，铸就属于你的传奇故事！这是一场勇气、智慧和力量的终极考验。在这个充满神秘、挑战和无尽荣耀的世界中，展现你的勇气和智慧，让你的名字响彻瓦尔哈拉！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298620/extras/636a63c07f3fc5fc5d9b163ef5770a96.poster.avif?t=1772096278\" width=600 height=181 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2298620/extras/636a63c07f3fc5fc5d9b163ef5770a96.webm?t=1772096278\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
